description: This is a fun and easy quiz that will help you master common Japanese words that are used when ordering sushi. Each quiz is only 3 multiple choice questions and the only requirement is an interest in the Japanese language and a love of sushi.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask sushi quiz to start a new game
name: Sushi Vocabulary Quiz
shortDescription: Practice vocabulary words for ordering sushi. Improve your understanding and appreciation of over 30 Japanese words.
